Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:32.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}BrushUP!!　ユウキ今日も　負けないハート磨くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:37.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)}Next Future　見逃さないで!
